column1: IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_b_cortolone_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_etio_d is MF 1 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 AND ccr_pt_d is MF 1 AND ccr_tha_d is MF 1 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_thdoc_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thaldo_d is MF 1 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 1  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 0
